description: Leen's Mobile Grubbery is bringing gorgeous gourmet eats to the South Dakota streets! Owned and operated by Chef Jason Spars, this food truck is on a mission to leave a lasting impression on your taste buds. Flavors from the Far East, South of the Border, the American Heartland, and beyond are what you'll find when you visit Leen's Mobile Grubbery, so stop by today!
name: Leen's Mobile Grubbery
